Package: chipMap
Type: Package
Title: Make heatmap of High throughput sequencing data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xons
Maintainer: Xons <gxandgx@gmail.com>
Description: This package is used to make heatmaps and metaPlots of ChIPseq (or other sequencing data, like MNase-seq).The plot can be centered at given TSS or peak center, sorted by occupancy, peak width or the distance to nearest TSS, can be coverage heatmap or enrichment (peak binding) profile.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Depends: R(>= 3.2.1)
Imports: GenomicRanges(>= 1.22.4),GenomicAlignments(>=
        1.6.3),rtracklayer(>= 1.30.2),IRanges,RColorBrewer(>=
        1.1-2),optparse
NeedsCompilation: no
Packaged: 2016-10-20 21:12:13 UTC; xig
